---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout locale="en" title="Terms - Nido's Gaming Stack" description="Terms and project notes for Nido's Gaming Stack.">
  <section class="container-page section-space">
    <p class="eyebrow">Terms</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-5xl font-semibold md:text-7xl">Terms</h1>
    <div class="mt-8 max-w-3xl space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-muted">
      <p>Projects published here are personal indie works and may change during development. Playtest builds can contain bugs, incomplete features, and placeholder content.</p>
      <p>TI Simulator uses fictional and original presentation. It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or built from assets owned by real tournaments, teams, players, Dota, Valve, or The International.</p>
      <p>中文说明：本站发布的项目为个人独立开发作品，测试版可能包含缺陷、未完成内容和占位资源。TI 模拟器采用架空化和原创化表达，不代表与任何真实赛事、公司、战队或选手存在关联。</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
